Package: esq.handsontable
Title: Interactive Data Tables with Handsontable for Shiny
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anastasia", "Kostiv", email = "anastasiia.kostiv.ext@esqlabs.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A powerful, reusable Handsontable wrapper for R Shiny applications.
    Provides interactive data tables with dropdowns, multi-select with sorting,
    validation, conditional cell disabling, context menu, and more. Built on
    'Handsontable' <https://handsontable.com/> and 'React' for a smooth,
    Excel-like editing experience.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/esqlabs/esq.handsontable
